title: Genesis - Seconds Out (Live) (m4a)
description:
Genesis&#039; second live album, recorded during the "Wind & Wuthering" and "A Trick Of The Tail" tours 1976-1977 (m4a):

DISC 1:
1. Squonk
2. The Carpet Crawlers
3. Robbery, Assault & Battery
4. Afterglow
5. Firth Of Fifth
6. I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)
7. The Lamb Lies Down On Broadway
8. The Musical Box (Closing Section)

DISC 2:
1. Supper&#039;s Ready
2. The Cinema Show
3. Dance On A Volcano
4. Los Endos

Lineup:
Phil Collins - lead vocals, drums, percussion
Steve Hackett - lead electric and acoustic guitars
Michael Rutherford - bass, guitars, bass pedals, vocals
Tony Banks - keyboards, acoustic 12-string, vocals
Bill Bruford - drums and percussion (disc 2, track 2)
Chester Thompson - drums and percussion (all others)

Enjoy!
